</string>
    </property>
    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;José Rizal’s life and death transcended his time. Though executed by the Spanish in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;1896&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;, his ideas lived on, igniting the flame of the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;Philippine Revolution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt; and inspiring future generations. Rizal’s sacrifices not only led to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;Philippine independence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt; but also helped shape a nation’s identity, promoting values of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;freedom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;equality&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;, and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;justice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;. Today, Rizal is celebrated as a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;martyr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt; and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;visionary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;, whose works continue to resonate, reminding Filipinos of the ongoing fight for the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;ideals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt; he cherished. His legacy is an enduring testament to the power of knowledge and nonviolent resistance in the pursuit of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;national unity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt; and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;self-determination&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#2f2018;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
